cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB 

The paper deals with document clustering and similarity measures, which are topics related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of external thesauruses like WordNet and the focus on semantics also suggest a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions experimental studies on text mining datasets, which could be related to machine learning (cs.LG) and databases (cs.DB).
